#. type: Plain text
#: source/server_admin/topics/roles/composite.adoc:19
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"Once you flip this switch the role selection UI will be displayed lower on the page and you'll be able to associate\n"
"realm level and client level roles to the composite you are creating.  In this example, the `employee` realm-level\n"
"role was associated with the `developer` composite role.  Any user with the `developer` role will now also inherit\n"
"the `employee` role too.\n"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: source/server_admin/topics/roles/composite.adoc:21
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"When tokens and SAML assertions are created, any composite will also have its associated roles added to the claims and\n"
"      assertions of the authentication response sent back to the client.\n"
msgstr ""
